{"tid":659848,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加國野生動物園員工擅帶熊隻外出被控","createTime":"2018-05-10T08:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T14:19:33.000Z","uid":141103,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0209f356dba31ebc480774def53a47bda0da9ae6","tid":659848,"uid":141103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:03:22.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】平時登山都可能見過有標語忠告「不要隨便餵飼野生動物」。而在外國的野生動物園，如果員工隨便帶園內的野生動物外出或餵飼，亦要負上法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n英國《衛報》報道，加拿大一個野生動物園因有員工在沒有知會當局下，擅自帶野生棕熊外出吃雪糕，被控違反《野生動物法》。<br />\n<br />\n位於艾伯塔省中部的野生動物園年初上載影片，顯示動物園員工帶同一隻一歲大的野生棕熊駕車外出，去到一間雪糕店時，小熊從車窗探頭，由雪糕店老闆親手餵食雪糕。<br />\n<br />\n片段引起很大爭議，有保護野生動物組織批評動物園做法不負責任，雖然有關片段已刪除，但這場風波似乎還未平息。<br />\n<br />\n艾伯塔省當局經調查後，指自從小熊去年從美國運到加拿大後，動物園員工曾多次將牠擅自帶離，違反《野生動物法》相關規定，指控動物園及負責人兩項罪名。<br />\n<br />\n動物園負責人承認做錯，又指事件顯示當局對動物園的規管嚴格是一件好事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=305305&amp;refer=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D305305%26refer%3Dshare&d=PptU2tuoabB7ai56lLI6GtZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=dfc1fe80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D305305%26refer%3Dshare&h=6a646571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=305305&amp;refer=share</a>"},{"pid":"627b8d3f227d68e67341a235bb8daea852563a3e","tid":659848,"uid":141103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:04:39.000Z","msg":"其實熊食唔食得雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ee92077392d7aaa8be7005512a8bb1fd71e25d","tid":659848,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T08:07:11.000Z","msg":"雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi